{"tid":1334766,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【圍城一刻我在現場】出口全封警察殺氣騰騰 女街坊憶述心驚的一幕","createTime":"2019-07-20T08:39:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T16:40:59.000Z","uid":14503,"like":6,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"57b41b25fd4984fa0b4f8386bd2fd3fdbd6f992b","tid":1334766,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:39:00.000Z","msg":"【圍城一刻我在現場】出口全封警察殺氣騰騰 女街坊憶述心驚的一幕<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1rTSDtH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1rTSDtH.jpg&h=a788eed8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n週日晚，沙田新城市廣場引發警民衝突，警方進駐驅散示威者爭議聲不絕，導致連日來有大批市民包圍新城市廣場要求交代事件。<br />\n<br />\n事發當晚，居於火炭的黃太在正身處於新城市廣場中庭位置，原打算購物，豈料卻跟防暴警察撞過正著，「四周都無出路，突然有人勸我不要再向前行，話就快打人，仲話我著黑色衫，我驚到連八達通都跌咗，我問差人邊條路無封，可否讓路畀我，我要行路返屋企。」但卻換來警察目怒兇光，殺氣騰騰的表情令她一生也無法忘記。「他畀我感覺係，你再講多一句話，我就動手，他揸住警棍，我即時想起朱經緯。」<br />\n<br />\n「我係70年代的人，一直很尊重警察，我教導子女都話警察叔叔係好的，但個仔話，你唔好再講警察好，我解釋不能一竹篙打一船人，但經過當晚以後，我唔會再咁講，因為佢眼神係想食咗我！」驚魂未定，為求盡快回家，她哀求一位沙田廣場的住户，帶她進入屋苑，從地下沙田正街岀口離開，再繞過街市斜路轉往單車徑，步行廿分鐘返回火炭家。<br />\n<br />\n經過漫長黑夜，她指身上的衣服內的汗水弄致鹽浮出來了，膽顫心驚，徹夜難眠。<br />\n<br />\n她有感而發地說：「我平時好少喺facebook發帖，都忍唔住要問，青年人點解咁好人，無整爛櫥窗玻璃，既然人哋話你係暴徒，你仲幫人哋抹地，香港青年係全世界最優秀嘅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中國人</span></strong>！」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：艾馬<br />\n<br />\n攝影：林頌華<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_682294_0?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1FCzbHWBUJrhjP4y0S3zbqmWgdmp2FXkUodRXH6cvUEMT92bumLJH6XbM&amp;code=5d32d1a63a408b00c1daa6d9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_682294_0%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1FCzbHWBUJrhjP4y0S3zbqmWgdmp2FXkUodRXH6cvUEMT92bumLJH6XbM%26code%3D5d32d1a63a408b00c1daa6d9&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbguBxQMtbc6xR8MkqxZcasw%3D&h=89867c7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_682294_0%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1FCzbHWBUJrhjP4y0S3zbqmWgdmp2FXkUodRXH6cvUEMT92bumLJH6XbM%26code%3D5d32d1a63a408b00c1daa6d9&h=2dac0c76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_682294_0?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1FCzbHWBUJrhjP4y0S3zbqmWgdmp2FXkUodRXH6cvUEMT92bumLJH6XbM&amp;code=5d32d1a63a408b00c1daa6d9</a><br />\n<br />\n成篇野都好正直到見到最後3隻字.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec4aa149a31fa0af3d803de38cab37fd1b112c9","tid":1334766,"uid":31780,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:40:38.000Z","msg":"最後三隻字真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93e7eda964868c5198e61de0c65adf213b1db37","tid":1334766,"uid":269148,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:41:15.000Z","msg":"無計 上一代大中華概念植根佢地思想"},{"pid":"552d880ee4ca85d9163d129ba416ced1343d0bb9","tid":1334766,"uid":231583,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyT